T02TD1746E:116a-1: karma mu dra pa r'iksha au pa de sha n'a ma /
T02TD1746E:116a-3: las kyi phyag rgya brtag pa'i man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD1746E:116a-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1746E:116a-5: mi mo dung gi rnal bkod dang //
T02TD1746E:116a-6: ba lang padmo'i rigs las byung //
T02TD1746E:116a-7: bye ba sum cu rtsa gnyis las //
T02TD1746E:116a-8: tha ma rnams par spang bar bya ;
T02TD1746E:116a-9: / de dag so so'i spyod pa dang //
T02TD1746E:116a-10: kha dog dbyibs dang mtshan ma dang //
T02TD1746E:116a-11: ngang tshul rnams las so so yi //
T02TD1746E:116a-12: rigs kyi mtshan nyid shes par bya //
T02TD1746E:116a-13: ser zhing dmar pa'i bud med gang //
T02TD1746E:116a-14: tshig snyan rtag par spyod lam mkhas //
T02TD1746E:116a-15: skad gdangs mthon pos smra byed cing //
T02TD1746E:116a-16: cog cog por ni 'dug la dga' //
T02TD1746E:116a-17: lta ba zur gyis gsal por 'dzin //
T02TD1746E:116a-18: tshig kyang zur gyis nges rtogs pa'i //
T02TD1746E:116a-19: bud med blo mchog de lta bu //
T02TD1746E:116a-20: rtag par dngos grub rnams kyi rgyu //
T02TD1746E:116a-21: ser zhing dkar ba'i bud med gang //
T02TD1746E:116a-22: lus ni dbye min sgu bo min //
T02TD1746E:116a-23: byin du yan lag thams cad legs //
T02TD1746E:116a-24: khyad par du yang smin phrag mdzes //
T02TD1746E:116a-25: bzhin 'phel chung zhing rngom chung la //
T02TD1746E:116a-26: ao sko'i dbyibs ni chud dgye yi //
T02TD1746E:116a-27: mdza' bo rtag tu sdug gyur pa //
T02TD1746E:116a-28: dbang phyug mi mo gnyis pa yin //
T02TD1746E:116a-29: bud med ser ba'i mdog ldan zhing //
T02TD1746E:116b-0: rtag par de'i mig po ma @116b che ;
T02TD1746E:116b-2: nam yang de yi tshig mi brtan //
T02TD1746E:116b-3: dbang po rno zhing brjed ngas chung //
T02TD1746E:116b-4: yid du 'ong ba'i skyes bu la //
T02TD1746E:116b-5: lta brtson byed kyang chad mi btsan //
T02TD1746E:116b-6: mi mo bsten bya min par gsungs //
T02TD1746E:116b-7: yid 'ong sngo bsangs kha dog can //
T02TD1746E:116b-8: mig dkyus ring zhing de rab mdzes //
T02TD1746E:116b-9: byad kyi gzang ring mchu skor che //
T02TD1746E:116b-10: bzhin dang lag par ri mo mang //
T02TD1746E:116b-11: dul zhing ngag snyan mnyen des che //
T02TD1746E:116b-13: 'dris pa rnams la gzhungs bzang zhing //
T02TD1746E:116b-14: bkra shis yan lag mi mo mchog / bud med autpala mdog 'dra zhing //
T02TD1746E:116b-15: lus gzar 'dril zhing sen mo zlum //
T02TD1746E:116b-16: mig yangs dkar zhing yid du 'ong //
T02TD1746E:116b-17: skra mnyen smra ba nyung ba'i bdag / skyes bu rnams la gus byed cing //
T02TD1746E:116b-18: brtson pa mthar phyin byed la brtson //
T02TD1746E:116b-19: khong yangs ston la mkhas gyur pa //
T02TD1746E:116b-21: byin du mdog nag dpral ba ser //
T02TD1746E:116b-22: mtshams mtha' dma' zhing rdzi ma mthug / bong thung yan lag rtsub pa dang //
T02TD1746E:116b-23: mig mi sdug cing smra ba mang //
T02TD1746E:116b-24: 'dum kha yang zhing chags la dga' //
T02TD1746E:116b-25: gang la skyes bu bzang ngan med //
T02TD1746E:116b-26: dri dang me bzad par ldan pa'i ;
T02TD1746E:116b-27: / bud med bsten pa nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD1746E:116b-28: bud gang zangs 'od rab mdzes shing //
T02TD1746E:116b-29: gang gi mgul pa yan lag ring //
T02TD1746E:116b-30: thung ngu ring po ma yin zhing //
T02TD1746E:116b-31: smin ma phra zhing smin phrag yangs //
T02TD1746E:116b-32: khong dal rtag par spyod lam gcig / rna ba bzang dang rab ldan zhing //
T02TD1746E:116b-33: so thags mnyam pa'i bud med ni //
T02TD1746E:116b-34: rtag tu yon tan ring mi 'gro //
T02TD1746E:116b-35: dmar ba'i zangs kyis mtshon pa yi //
T02TD1746E:116b-36: bzhin ba zangs sdom zhing cung zad sbom //
T02TD1746E:116b-37: drang zhing lus khyim legs pa dang //
T02TD1746E:116b-38: shin tu brla dang ro smad rgyas //
T02TD1746E:116b-39: rang don nyams pa rnam par spang //
T02TD1746E:116b-40: bslu bar mi nus khong shes che //
T02TD1746E:116b-41: skra dang ba spu ring ldan pa'i //
T02TD1746E:116b-42: bu mo longs spyod pa zhig yin //
T02TD1746E:116b-43: mdog dmar spyod lam chos la dga' //
T02TD1746E:116b-44: mtho dman tshig dang spyod lam can //
T02TD1746E:116b-45: rtag par smra la dga' byed cing //
T02TD1746E:116b-46: phyin ci log tu ston par byed //
T02TD1746E:117a-2: gtong dang mi ldan 'jungs pa dang //
T02TD1746E:117a-3: chags dang sdang ba mang ba yi //
T02TD1746E:117a-4: bud med skyon gyi dri ma can //
T02TD1746E:117a-5: dmar zhing dkar ba'i bud med gang //
T02TD1746E:117a-6: sbom zhing phra ba'i skabs dang ldan //
T02TD1746E:117a-7: nu ma brla dang ro smad rgyas //
T02TD1746E:117a-8: ske dang rked pa sor mo ring //
T02TD1746E:117a-9: so dang sen mo mnyam ldan zhing //
T02TD1746E:117a-10: tshigs zlum byin pa bags kyi phra //
T02TD1746E:117a-11: lte ba'i 'og phyogs drang ldan pa'i //
T02TD1746E:117a-12: ba spu'i phreng ba gyen du langs //
T02TD1746E:117a-13: lte khung zab cing pad dbyibs 'dra //
T02TD1746E:117a-14: skye gnas mtho zhing bu ga rub //
T02TD1746E:117a-15: dal gyis mig ni rdeb byed pa'i //
T02TD1746E:117a-16: mi mo dbang phyug dpal gyi gzhi ;
T02TD1746E:117a-17: / bud gang kunda ltar dkar zhing //
T02TD1746E:117a-18: rus pa rags shing lus stobs can //
T02TD1746E:117a-19: rtag par mngal du bu pho 'chags //
T02TD1746E:117a-20: spyod lam dal zhing mdzes dang ldan //
T02TD1746E:117a-22: phrad par dka' zhing bral dka' ba'i //
T02TD1746E:117a-23: bu mo gsang thub blo gros can //
T02TD1746E:117a-24: sngags pa rnams kyis smad mi bya //
T02TD1746E:117a-25: bud gang dkar zhing dregs dang ldan //
T02TD1746E:117a-26: de ni ngo bzhin skyon med kyang //
T02TD1746E:117a-27: skyes bu rnams kyis spong bar 'gyur //
T02TD1746E:117a-28: phra zhing mig ni bsgyur la dga' //
T02TD1746E:117a-29: rked rags rked pa sbom pa dang //
T02TD1746E:117a-30: byad sogs 'chos shing byi dor brtson //
T02TD1746E:117a-31: rgod cing bslu bar sla ba yi //
T02TD1746E:117a-32: bu mo bsten par ma gsungs so //
T02TD1746E:117a-33: rigs rnams las ni thams cad la //
T02TD1746E:117a-34: bsten dang bsten min shes byas nas //
T02TD1746E:117a-35: yon tan ldan pa'i skye gnas su //
T02TD1746E:117a-36: mkhas pa rnams kyis bde ba btsal //
T02TD1746E:117a-37: de rnyed gyur nas rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1746E:117a-38: 'du longs g-yeng ba kun sdangs nas ;
T02TD1746E:117a-39: / kun stong rab tu zhu mnyam pa //
T02TD1746E:117a-40: man ngag can gyis rtag tu bsam //
T02TD1746E:117a-41: 'jig rten kun nas khyab gnas pa'i //
T02TD1746E:117a-42: ji snyed mi mor 'gyur ba yi //
T02TD1746E:117a-43: bha ga rtsa yi khyad par gyis //
T02TD1746E:117a-44: bcu phyed du ni rnam par grags //
T02TD1746E:117a-45: rlugs dang dung dang khva gdong dang //
T02TD1746E:117a-46: za byed gdong dang padmo can //
T02TD1746E:117a-47: gang dag padma'i rtsa sbu bas ni //
T02TD1746E:117a-48: shin tu yangs ma rlugs mar brjod //
T02TD1746E:117a-49: rtsa sbubs 'bros shing dog pa yis //
T02TD1746E:117a-50: zug rdu skye 'gyur dung can ma //
T02TD1746E:117a-51: bud med gang gi padma'i nang //
T02TD1746E:117a-52: rtsub cing tsha ba khva gdong can //
T02TD1746E:117b-0: bde ba yod dang med pa'i bdag / rtsa sbu bas zha @117b bo za byed gdong //
T02TD1746E:117b-1: bha ga padmo ltar sdud cing //
T02TD1746E:117b-2: padma snal ltar phra mo can //
T02TD1746E:117b-3: de ltar padma'i khyad par las //
T02TD1746E:117b-5: padmo can mchog rlugs ma dang //
T02TD1746E:117b-6: dung can ma ni bar ma'o //
T02TD1746E:117b-7: za byed gdong dang khva ta'i gdong //
T02TD1746E:117b-8: skyon rnams spang bar dka' ba'i phyir ;
T02TD1746E:117b-9: / bha ga rnams las tha mar 'gyur //
T02TD1746E:117b-10: tha ma smad pas mi blang ngo //
T02TD1746E:117b-11: bha ga'i nang na gnas pa yi //
T02TD1746E:117b-13: rab tu shin tu phra ba'i rtsa //
T02TD1746E:117b-14: ring po 'bring du gsungs pa yin //
T02TD1746E:117b-15: de ltar rigs dang bha ga dang //
T02TD1746E:117b-16: rtsa rnams rab 'bring tha ma las ;
T02TD1746E:117b-17: / rab dang 'bring po'ang bsten bya zhing //
T02TD1746E:117b-18: tha ma rtag tu spang bar bya //
T02TD1746E:117b-19: tha ma rtags kyis lus zungs nyams //
T02TD1746E:117b-20: de nyams bde ba nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD1746E:117b-21: de yis ting 'dzin mchog las nyams //
T02TD1746E:117b-22: de phyir mkhas pas sman pa yin //
T02TD1746E:117b-23: rnal 'byor ma yi rgyud chen las //
T02TD1746E:117b-24: rigs kyi dbye ba rgyas pa dang //
T02TD1746E:117b-25: mtshan ma la sogs gsungs pa las //
T02TD1746E:117b-26: 'dir ni man ngag bsdus pa yin //
T02TD1746E:117b-27: las kyi phyag rgya brtag pa'i man ngag ces bya ba /
T02TD1746E:117b-28: pandi ta aa mo gha badzra las byung ba rdzogs so /
T02TD1746E:117b-30: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po de nyid dang /
T02TD1746E:117b-31: bod kyi lo ts'a ba 'gos lhas btsas kyis bsgyur ba'o//
